        mockingjay
        ===============================
        
        .. image:: https://travis-ci.org/kevinjqiu/mockingjay.svg?branch=master
                :target: https://travis-ci.org/kevinjqiu/mockingjay
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/mockingjay.svg
